name: Sigourney Wiener
description: In the cold expanse of space, a derelict ship whispered secrets. Sigourney Weiner, interstellar hotdog and explorer, took the challenge head-on. What awaited were not treasures or ancient secrets, but a legion of alien franks, thirsting for conquest. Victorious, she found herself in an alternate dimension, where heroes are celebrated with worlds named in their honor, her tales of bravery echoed across the stars. Now she must return to her home on the moon in her crypto powered spaceship.
